Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的暗号非常难解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星和犯人的名字一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要看穿望远镜深处的奥秘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.70,0:00:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.90,0:00:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.70,0:01:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了进行天体观测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.50,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来到了深山中的旅店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.00,0:02:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了店主天土陵司先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.80,0:02:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外还有收到邀请信而来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫悦子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川肇先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.50,0:02:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,及御上平八先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.00,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去了附近能看星星的山丘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然发现了变成白骨的尸体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且尸体的附近留着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.40,0:02:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由6根香烟传达的死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.50,0:02:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且那天夜里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.50,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是同样的死亡讯息吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.00,0:02:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.70,0:02:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟多了1根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星和香烟的暗号（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.80,0:02:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟变成了7根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.90,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们白天找到的这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1年前被杀的那位河野先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他留下的6根香烟所指的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和二川先生的7根香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.30,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所指的可能是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.90,0:03:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是犯人为了扰乱搜查视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.70,0:03:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地多放了1根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们听到了有什么东西掉到地上的声音后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.50,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上赶来这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跑过来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.90,0:03:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里附近看不见任何的亮光吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 确实是漆黑一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害河野先生和二川先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是同一个人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是二川先生想留下什么提示…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有1根沾有血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握着香烟盒的手指上也有血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口袋里的另一个香烟盒上也有血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.50,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侦探团徽章在响哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.30,0:04:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里没有人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 没有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.80,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没遇到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是找到了别人丢失的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢失的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面还留着未发出去的邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.20,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗 遗书吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死 死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.30,0:04:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该是从悬崖上摔下来后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就死亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.30,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在悬崖上留有二川先生的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.40,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且里边还有封
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,标题为遗书没有收信人的邮件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手机里留下遗书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗书是这样写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家请到这个旅店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了向当时都在这里的大家坦白我1年前所干的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 1年前杀害河野麻雄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是我 二川肇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是他未婚妻的野之宫小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺走了对你很重要的人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.20,0:05:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野的大学前辈天土陵司先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.60,0:05:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你经营的旅店蒙受了污名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.50,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是御上平八主编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.20,0:05:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我死后《Space Sunday》就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会死的原因是在悬崖上我与他起了争执
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.90,0:05:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推了他一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果他运气不好就失足掉下悬崖了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想只要说出实情应该可以得到大家的原谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.60,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却怎么也说不出口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.30,0:05:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决心在明天警察到来之前以死赎罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川肇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 果然还是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.30,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻雄他… 麻雄他真的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.10,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为上司的我也要道歉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.30,0:06:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悦子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他突然不见的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.00,0:06:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和犯人的身份都明白了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是留下遗书自杀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会留下这样的东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从悬崖上掉下来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川叔叔手里握着的7根香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野先生的是6根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是多了1根长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害河野先生的如果是二川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.00,0:06:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若他发现了河野先生留下的讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是自己而自杀的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么香烟的根数应该不会增加是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.20,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.60,0:06:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只有增加的1根上沾了血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有二川先生的手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.60,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和口袋里的另一个烟盒上也都沾有血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.40,0:06:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上还有被铁管之类的东西殴打过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被殴打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想血迹大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.50,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手按住出血的头部时沾到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 这7根香烟是有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.30,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在悬崖上把二川先生打倒并夺走手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面输入刚才的遗书时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生趁机往他事先带在身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装了6根香烟的烟盒里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放进了特地从另一个烟盒里拿出的1根香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要让人知道它是死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.80,0:07:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着装有6根香烟的香烟盒那是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想试试看河野先生的死亡讯息是不是指自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7根香烟 天土先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人不就是指你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御上先生你的名字是平八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是7根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你名字的首字母缩写不也是7根吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫悦子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要伤和气嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们3人在森林里没见过面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就让我们检查一下你们的房间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.90,0:08:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人应该藏着用来打死二川先生的铁管之类的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想等一会儿犯人再用这个来袭击我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不要翻得乱七八糟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.00,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 叔叔原来带着望远镜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是编辑部里的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜筒 镜座 寻星镜还有三脚架…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望远镜的镜筒还不至于硬到可以打人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.90,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且用那个三脚架打人的话是会弯曲变形的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔也用香烟试着解过死亡讯息了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是没解出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们适可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到什么时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.10,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像凶器的只有这把伞了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是伞上没有任何地方弯曲变形啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.90,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐带着的酒瓶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢在森林里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.30,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们和我擦肩而过的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.70,0:09:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦肩而过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你们不是来追我的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那个长了雀斑的男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个娃娃头的小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我感觉很不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在树荫下呕吐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.60,0:09:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一直在考虑河野先生的死亡讯息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.40,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有想到是那个叫二川的人的名字缩写
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.20,0:09:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不知道他后面的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么剩下来的只有天土先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过对你来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.50,0:09:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个旅店都好像是你的房间一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以还是早上叫警察来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托他们搜查了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方来的时候 要请他们顺便也搜一下森林里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.30,0:09:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是犯人就会把罪证扔在森林里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.40,0:10:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.80,0:10:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生的房间里到处都搜过了 但没找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前说要找的那个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下那样的遗书再把人杀害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会有那样东西的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.50,0:10:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你们在去检查房间的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直监视着等在这里的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑啊 那个叫天土的叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 很可疑 很可疑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.40,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.20,0:10:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他一直目不转睛地看着旅客登记簿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很仔细地看了好几遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是这种可怕的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登记簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.90,0:10:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御上先生和二川先生都说过 遇到河野先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.20,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那么一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.30,0:10:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野先生失踪后他们两人也来了几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫河野的人失踪的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.60,0:11:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河野先生和野之宫小姐的名字后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御上先生和二川先生的名字也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这莫非是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.70,0:11:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.50,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙纱绘牌(Fusae)的钱包 这么大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.80,0:11:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿这个来换我就帮忙 怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.40,0:11:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.70,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.30,0:11:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是盲肠炎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛吗 小哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是真糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话又不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算背下山也要好几个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊 博士 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士 救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛啊 博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 能叫救护车吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 请叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话线不是不见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的地址是群马县的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.10,0:12:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点叫救护车小哀就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.90,0:12:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚才只是在演戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了让藏起电话线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还放掉汽车轮胎的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.50,0:13:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把我们困在这里的人现身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以麻雄的名义给我们寄去邀请信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我们聚集在这里的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.50,0:13:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在二川先生的手机里留下遗书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.30,0:13:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其伪装成自杀的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他从悬崖上推下去的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.50,0:13:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天土陵司先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.80,0:13:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家召集到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将大家困在此地的确实是天土先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不是杀人犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.20,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.30,0:13:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人留在手机中的遗书里提到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请大家的是二川自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.50,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果天土先生是杀害二川先生的凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会让我们认为把大家困在这里的是二川先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会把那根电话线藏在二川先生的衣服里或房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天土先生把大家叫到这里是因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他发现了1年前在这里失踪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野先生的白骨和他的戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.70,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及香烟的死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.10,0:14:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看了一眼散乱的香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.20,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能正确地说出香烟有四根长的和两根短的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.40,0:14:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现那些东西之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.70,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才向那天住在这里的人发去了邀请信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要犯人知道我们已经发现了遗骨和死亡讯息的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.50,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会出来自首的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果二川先生死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话就没能说出口……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.30,0:14:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来杀害二川先生的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.00,0:14:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人不就是那个叫野之宫的姐姐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.30,0:14:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.30,0:14:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果注意到香烟表示的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生名字首字母缩写的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.60,0:15:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对杀害自己恋人的犯人复仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.70,0:15:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动机十分充足呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫小姐说过在森林里和我们3人擦肩而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要赶在我们前面与二川先生在悬崖上会面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.50,0:15:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并把他推下去是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.00,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们3人在二川先生坠崖的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是马上赶到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.70,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候如果她从悬崖上看到你们的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从悬崖上能看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是豆粒般大小的3个手电筒的灯光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.60,0:15:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中不可能分辨是哪3个人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.80,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.50,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用排除法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是二川先生上司的御上平八主编
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以犯人就只能是你了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.70,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说因为其他两个人不是犯人所以我就是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.80,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是二川先生握着的香烟变成了7根啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.90,0:15:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是表示你的名字平八的讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是巧合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么一定要杀死他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果他1年前杀害了那个叫河野的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.20,0:16:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就更没理由杀他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.60,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为只见过一次面的人报仇 没道理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这只是在假设二川先生杀害了河野先生的前提下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.90,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了这本登记簿发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.70,0:16:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御上先生的名字在河野先生后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.90,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以河野先生只知道"御上"的读音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道读音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御上先生的"御"是御手洗（卫生间）的"御"吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.50,0:16:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常会想到"三上"(注:"三上"和"衘上"日语同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔画数是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.60,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6画
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野先生留下的6根香烟和二川先生留下的7根香烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.70,0:17:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是暗示"三上平八"名字的死亡讯息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.40,0:17:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生多加了1根是为了让人更容易明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.60,0:17:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一牌子的香烟不正暗示了两个案件的犯人是同一个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.40,0:17:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川先生看登记簿的时候还笑了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个时候发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害河野先生的是御上先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.10,0:17:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后二川先生为了确认这个事实才遭杀害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有这样的证据呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.70,0:17:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据就是在你房间里的这个包里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.30,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果从中找到打倒二川先生的类似铁管的凶器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能成为决定性的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.70,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.80,0:17:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个包刚才不是查过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 铁管虽然没有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也没有某样东西哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.60,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某样东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望远镜的配重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在这个镜筒里放入了其它什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把配重拿掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.50,0:18:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为的是让重量保持和原来一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么能不能让我们看看镜筒里面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么擦拭也应该会出现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.70,0:18:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因打死二川先生而沾到血迹所引起的鲁米诺反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还沾得到处都是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二川的血迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易提拔他当了编辑部主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他却威胁我说若不想被人发现你杀人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.80,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给我五千万日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我只是惩罚了那个忘恩负义的河野而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.20,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.70,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.10,0:18:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1年前的那天 叫河野的男人来拜托我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.40,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他让我帮他确认其发现的彗星是不是新的彗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.70,0:18:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就是以你名字命名的那颗彗星吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.40,0:18:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他找到的我 让我到悬崖上帮他确认的那颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.40,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你为了独占彗星的冠名权才把麻雄他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.10,0:19:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托他把我的名字也加进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.00,0:19:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他却… 忘恩负义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.80,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定彗星的名字叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.10,0:19:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"天土 野之宫 河野 彗星"了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.10,0:19:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没想到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.90,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.10,0:19:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那天说过"终于遇见了"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.80,0:19:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以为他一定喜欢上了其他的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是在孩童时代就一直等待着那一天的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.00,0:19:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而那个人却固执地不听我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.80,0:19:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我说看谁先申请成功吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在想要回旅店时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人却追过来拉住我 我只是用力挣脱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然从悬崖上掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后过了几天你再来旅店时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把石灰撒在尸体上让它加速变成白骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.60,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.50,0:19:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是让我吃了一惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄来邀请信的居然是天土先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还一直认为是二川呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点拿出来啊 铁管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.20,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要催我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.50,0:20:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这铁管可不是一般的铁管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.80,0:20:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霰弹枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你们几个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站到那边排成一排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死二川的时候为了不让你们听到枪声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是打晕了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都这样了 你们就一起去死吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死你们后 需要大量石灰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.00,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一瞬间就把你变成天上的星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.40,0:20:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没看到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在穿鞋子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你还逃得掉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.40,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我和叔叔一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.70,0:20:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的鞋子也不是普通的鞋子哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.40,0:21:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.40,0:21:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字永远被记录下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为与星星同名的罪犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.70,0:22:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.40,0:22:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么河野先生那么固执地坚持那个星星的名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.20,0:22:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫小姐是他的恋人这是一定要加进去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但把天土先生换成御上先生的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.10,0:23:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不会有这种事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.30,0:23:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是3人是大学时代的前辈和后辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.90,0:23:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定关系很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.00,0:23:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.70,0:23:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不只是这样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也分不开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.10,0:23:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天土的"天"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.30,0:23:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野之宫的"之"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.30,0:23:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河野的"河"排在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.70,0:23:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就变成"天之河"(银河)了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.60,0:23:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.30,0:23:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不愧是柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们能不能给我安静一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.40,0:23:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜三更的被叫出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.40,0:23:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得休假准备到乡下的奶奶家去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不得不推迟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.90,0:23:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我困死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.40,0:23:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在往哪里打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.20,0:23:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在往哪里打电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.80,0:23:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟取县的奶奶那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.30,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸟取县…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.30,0:24:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.50,0:24:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.20,0:24:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.50,0:24:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这个警笛声是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.30,0:24:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.20,0:24:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.70,0:24:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时限15点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.30,0:24:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.40,0:24:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帐篷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.90,0:24:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双休日的作业已经没时间做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.40,0:24:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经是星期一的晚上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.70,0:24:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 我要看柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.70,0:24:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚已经结束了